OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist patches will quickly
OL,6,Fclear this morning to leave a dry and
OL,7,Fsunny day across the region. Feeling
OL,8,Fhot with high levels of UV and light
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining dry this evening
OL,12,Fwith plenty of late evening sunshine.
OL,13,FOvernight may see a few mist patches
OL,14,Freform but most remaining clear.
OL,15,FStaying warm with temperatures only
OL,16,Fslowly falling away.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
