OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FThe heatwave continues on
OL,6,FSaturday with another dry and sunny
OL,7,Fday. Feeling hot with high UV but a
OL,8,Fmore notable breeze developing
OL,9,Fthroughout the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,12,FRemaining largely dry and sunny
OL,13,Fthroughout, although a small chance of
OL,14,Fthe odd thunderstorm developing from
OL,15,FMonday. Staying hot, although an
OL,16,Feasterly breeze will bring a little
OL,17,Frelief in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
